movie.title: Clambake
movie.description_intro: Scott Heyward, whose the son of a millionaire, is tired of woman fawning over him because of his wealth, meets Tom, who's on his way to his new job as a water skiing instructor at a hotel. They envy each other's life and decide to switch places. So Scott pretends to be Tom and Tom lives it up pretending to be Scott. Scott meets Dianne who is trying to land a rich guy and when playboy James Jamison catches her eye, she asks Scott to help her snag him. Scott agrees to but finds himself attracted to her. Scott also decides to build a boat for a speedboat race that's going to take place in the hotel but he's using a new experimental chemical which doesn't hold in water, which his father forbade him to use.

movies.title: Alabama Snake
movies.summary: Alabama Snake explores the story of Oct. 4, 1991, when a violent crime was reported in the town of Scottsboro, Alabama. Glenn Summerford, a Pentecostal minister, was accused of attempting to murder his wife with a rattlesnake. The details of the investigation and the trial that followed have "haunted Southern Appalachia for decades." Alabama Snake features local historian and folklorist, Thomas Burton, who has spent his life studying the culture, beliefs, and folklore of Pentecostal snake handlers, painting a "Southern Gothic portrait" of Summerford and his tale of demon possession.

movies.title: Hunter's Creed
movies.summary: After losing his wife to cancer, Dave Bryant also lost his faith in God. In an effort to lift his spirits, Dave's old church buddies convince him to participate in the hunting show they've always wanted to make together. The group heads to a remote cabin and begins documenting their experiences. Before long, Dave senses a dark presence in the woods he's convinced is stalking him. But the other guys have no idea what he's talking about, and Dave begins to wonder if it's all in his head. The presence continues closing in, eventually bringing Dave face to face with death - and his faith.

movies.title: The Babysitter: Killer Queen
movies.summary: Two years after Cole survived a satanic blood cult, he's living another nightmare: high school. And the demons from his past? Still making his life hell.

movies.title: Free Style
movies.summary: Cale Bryant is determined to win a coveted spot on the Grand National motocross racing team. With the support of his loving mother, precocious little sister and new girlfriend, Cale proves against all odds that he has the heart, the willpower and the courage never to give up on his dream.
